ComicInfo.Summary: For the first time since Hell came to Earth, Bethany is unprotected by Belial. As she and Bloato maneuver through the new American wilderness they discover the world is nothing as it once was. With this realization, what was left of Bethany's hope and spirit is crushed. Can she muster the will to travel across this barren, scorched earth in hopes of a reprieve from God? Probably, she's pretty awesome.
ComicInfo.Title: Back to the Old House
